Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 我到底还能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了改变那如狭隘庭园般的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还活不到人生的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗 相拥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在无意识中被刻上的经验纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当站在悬崖边的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.47,0:00:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦难抓住了我的手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到了自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往更加宽广的领域\N往更深更大的某处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着无法预测的世界前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And lt's calling me again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.17,0:01:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12月的平均气温为23度？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.05,0:01:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以游泳了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.14,0:01:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次旅游会很有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.14,0:01:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会允许那个人做独家采访呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.06,0:01:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后和自卫队的联合作战任务会增加
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.27,0:01:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的秘密武器迟早也会曝光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.07,0:01:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再者，口头上的敷衍还是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.95,0:01:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.24,0:02:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.95,0:02:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿！能来这个南方小岛我很高兴，不过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.95,0:02:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于实地的采访…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.75,0:02:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会派一位很可爱的人做你的向导
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.17,0:02:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太期待了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！看到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇，那就是人类的堡垒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对MU作战的最前线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.05,0:02:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根来彼方岛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.07,0:02:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是一个抽象艺术品？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.86,0:02:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是从奈里亚神殿遗迹中运回来的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你违反了守密原则
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里都是相关人员
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.66,0:02:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来要做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.25,0:02:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要担心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心？我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，来试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许如月博士知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人好像什么都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不清楚它的构造是怎样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.55,0:04:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然她不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑道和机库均已清理至4级
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有硬件方面的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与无人战机的协作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和地球联合使用的程序\N我们差不多都可以适应了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大的问题在于维护保养部门
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对他们不满意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的技术的确不错，但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无人战机没有灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵魂啊命运啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出生在20世纪的人就喜欢那样虚幻的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白人的坏毛病就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只相信能看见的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:04:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想让我在客厅里放些黄色的东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们两年来的第一次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你们都一点没变
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？真是有两年没见了呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你邀我来这个小队，bunga mawar
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:21.15,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}bunga mawar：印尼语，蔷薇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是艾尔菲·哈迪亚特中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天开始，被任命为TERRA空军Alpha小队队长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说了，祝你好运，中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾尔菲·哈迪亚特中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，是那个唯一从Overlord行动中\N生还的飞行员吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸运女神？不，或者是死神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:05:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.44,0:06:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个美人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo Jupiter里面怎么样啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.65,0:06:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京塔真的是蓝的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时间的话我一定要听听你的经历
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去过管理部了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.95,0:06:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们让你到任后就去那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.67,0:06:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威风凛凛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打赌她是个“女神”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢赌博
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把现场的事情都扔给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的，从本州带来的纪念品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.14,0:06:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，多谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢甜食
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有，我想让你给别人当一回向导
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向导？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此，他就是那个“可爱的人”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是天户通讯的贰神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们允许我对TERRA进行采访
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么带他在人工岛转转就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦了，如果可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！五味君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.05,0:07:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些是从本州带的纪念品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都没变啊，亘理先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有轻微的震动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近来他挺合作嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独自离开了故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个为拯救世界而战的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讽刺的语气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你误会了，我真是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能进来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，请进
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把衣服放在那里就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，再见…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七森小姐，你和遥关系很好，是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，但我们还算不上挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥喜欢什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.27,0:08:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她喜欢喝酒，我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为圣诞节准备吗？\N不问小惠的爱好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她比较容易了解…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里和东京的差别并没有那么大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和家人分开后，不孤单吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.45,0:08:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真觉得痛苦，也没必要强忍着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊，你今天要调到战术部去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.55,0:08:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.18,0:08:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人君吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他做的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说在分析部门进行实验时很合作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已经适应了岛上的生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外的，他很坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.15,0:08:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道他是不是遇上了好人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？这是八云君的经验么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总一，那个记者怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个，处理了一些事情后就立刻去采访了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.86,0:08:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去本岛了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到根来岛？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.16,0:09:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要留在这里一阵子\N他说要去找一个以后可以常去的商店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人到这里来干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.96,0:09:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是联合军的监察官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来监视你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.18,0:09:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不记得了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们半夜一起偷跑出去…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你来找我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是以失败告终
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那些人中间你不感觉内心空虚吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我一直都是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这种冷漠无情的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是冷漠无情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我拿一瓶了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.35,0:10:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个，那样是喝不到的，因为有个小球堵着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得把它转到凹槽里面去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在度假吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单身赴任
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工薪族很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说这个你能明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.17,0:10:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以多少我还能理解一点的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？那个…我开车，之后把比萨饼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送比萨吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还有这种活啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.05,0:10:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“D-1出现，马上返回”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.77,0:10:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要工作了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，再会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个空瓶子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便的话，退给商店可以拿到退瓶费
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在太平洋上确认的D-1全高为6000米
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它正以40公里的时速向根来彼方岛前进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预计作战时间为1408
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1408是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，那个\N那个是指14点08分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据现在大约20分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标D-1很可能为两足步行型
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据推测腿和生长出来的部分长度约为5千米
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左右两边的形状应该是完全相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？为什么只有腿说明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只能看到腿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是这房子的主人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以打扰你一会儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现目标
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从11点到13点方向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离10000
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-1影像确认，在12点方向，情况确认
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各机维持队形接近目标
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon在后方待机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解！了解！了解！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要为我同伴的死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:12:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击中了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，还没结束
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它不是站着的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是飘浮着的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被外形误导了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alpha和Bravo，在16点方向散开！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blue队形
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.07,0:13:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风水不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人住？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.58,0:13:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.16,0:13:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名牌上有三个不同的姓氏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是亲戚吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.88,0:14:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个侄女和一个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盾牌？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能依靠孩子的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全国小学生绘画比赛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2009年的参加者名单里…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有神名绫人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:14:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候他五年级…\N如果现在还活着的话就有29岁了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我这里的绫人只有17岁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.27,0:15:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说，另有其人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.26,0:15:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-1咏叹调
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退！让Alpha-1队撤回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alpha-1队没有回音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要再…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon正在放出量子波
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在歌唱？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧，艾尔菲小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管我，注意敌人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人君！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心，只要他在座舱里就不会被电击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon活动停止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机师的生命维持降低至3级！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人君，请回答！绫人君！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人君！绫人君！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人君！听到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请快回答
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.37,0:17:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快，不做点什么的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以动吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人君！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.27,0:17:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.65,0:17:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差一点…！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚开！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚开！滚开！滚开！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚开！滚开！滚开！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo…Jupiter？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响亮的音色…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不存在于战争之火中…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.85,0:19:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你错了，olin
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一局如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.74,0:19:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有机会我会再来拜访的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六道博士…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单机突入不明云层！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.16,0:19:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自作主张是违反军纪的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种战斗方式是会让你送命的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己的命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你！你是认真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.55,0:19:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要单机突入
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为指挥官，我按最佳方式进行了判断
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.35,0:19:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你是违反了军纪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁闭两天，就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:19:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.87,0:20:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样如何，监察官先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得我们很无耻吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让一个被绑架来的孩子为我们作战
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.77,0:20:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想，这次该轮到我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.65,0:20:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后还请照顾他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不能上战场
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.47,0:21:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您一直在这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.76,0:21:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服的风，不知不觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹吹风，可以使人心情舒畅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.07,0:21:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.86,0:21:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为家境问题？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.66,0:21:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.37,0:21:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京在哪个方向…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.25,0:21:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是感觉它们之间有某种联系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.34,0:21:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.94,0:23:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥远的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.94,0:23:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耸立的纯白冰树
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.86,0:23:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱着黑暗心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.07,0:23:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon第八乐章
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.36,0:23:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰封圣诞夜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.87,0:23:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界饱含着声音


